tion to vaccinate and wear a mask, but both are your choice! It is up to you to save the party people!\n\nVirus Popper Reopened is FREE and Includes:\n\u25cf  4 New Maps!\n\u25cf  Over 15 funky weapons!\n\u25cf  8 Types of Viruses!\n\u25cf  Progression Unlocks\n\u25cf  Original Virus Popper game mode", "short_description": "Greetings Space Traveler, we need you to save the universe again! New virus variants threaten our galaxy. Level up with a new arsenal of weapons to combat them!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.starcadearcadellc.com/virus-popper-privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.starcadearcadellc.com/virus-popper-eula", "publisher_name": "Starcade Arcade LLC", "support_website_url": "https://www.starcadearcadellc.com/contact", "website_url": "https://www.starcadearcadellc.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "ARCADE", "CASUAL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "407399464520266"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974653_674633740566921_5950792480057875671_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=frLrEODnpTIQ7kNvgG74YEZ&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=As4jjmRxsC5gltm9t7s5y2f&oh=00_AYDmOj-NDGufsdZwcMrX8EHmD1wJJca1zZZoJ9fYZIOKKA&oe=66D2FE72"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Virus Popper", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": 